== Overview ==
Terminal based Instant Messagin center. Upstream/official homepage: http://www.centerim.org/

This is version Centerim 4.22.6 (has been released 2008-10-26)

Features:

* Jabber (gmail)
* ICQ
* IRC
* RSS feeds
* Sounds (with external player e.g. mplayer)
* Open URLS (with external browser e.g. dillo)

